133
00:15:54,203 --> 00:15:55,575
atau "Apa kau sudah makan?"

134
00:15:56,672 --> 00:15:58,545
Tapi, "Apa kau baik-baik saja?"

135
00:16:02,712 --> 00:16:03,885
Kau lihat...

136
00:16:05,014 --> 00:16:07,255
